         | "Hindi" #(i.e. 'Arabic' as used in Egypt)
         | "Kannada"
         | "Khmer"
         | "Malayalam"
         | "Oriya"
         | "Tamil"
         | "Telugu"
         | "Thai"
         | "Tibetan")

